window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Acclaimed author Guy Gavriel Kay has been honored with the World Fantasy Award for Best Novel (<i>Ysabel</i>) and the International Goliardos Award for his work in fantasy.&nbsp;</p> <p>Eight of the nine Palm provinces of the Peninsula have been overcome by warrior sorcerers Brandin and Alberico. But the sorcerers don't know that a small band of survivors is plotting their removal. With tensions mounting, the sorcerers become increasingly at odds as each decides where his own path - and that of the land - should truly lie.&nbsp;</p> <p>\"Brilliant. Rich in intrigue and subtlety. A gracefully plotted story. Highly recommended.\" (<i>Library Journal</i>)</p>"; 
